Package classes

Class SchoolClass

java.lang.Object
classes.SchoolClass
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SchoolClass extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a school class, including details such as class name, students, subject teachers, subjects offered, and a timetable. This class provides methods for managing these aspects, such as adding or removing students and teachers, and managing subjects.

      public void addSubject(Subject subject, Teacher teacher)

      Parameters:
      subject - The subject to be added.
      teacher - The teacher for the subject.

    • removeSubject

      public void removeSubject(Subject subject)
      Removes a subject from the class. If the subject is in the class's subject list, it is removed along with its corresponding teacher.
      Parameters:
